<main>
  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>To provide full functionality, <strong>SLD</strong> collects the following data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Discord User IDs</li>
    <li>Server (Guild) IDs</li>
    <li>Channel IDs and Role IDs</li>
    <li>Message IDs (for logging purposes, if enabled)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>SLD does <strong>not</strong> collect passwords, emails, payment info, or cookies, and does not access data outside Discord.</p>

  <h2>2. Message Content</h2>
  <p>Message content is read only to process commands, moderation filters, and logging if enabled by the server administrator. Content is <strong>not permanently stored</strong> unless logging is enabled. The bot does not share or sell this data outside Discord.</p>

  <h2>3. How We Use Data</h2>
  <p>Data is used strictly for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Executing commands (music, moderation, utilities)</li>
    <li>Logging moderation actions</li>
    <li>Server configuration and auto-role systems</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
  <p>Data is stored securely and access is restricted to the bot developer(s) only.</p>

  <h2>5. User Rights</h2>
  <p>Server administrators and users may:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Request removal of server data</li>
    <li>Disable bot features or remove the bot from the server</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Contact</h2>
  <p>For questions or data deletion requests, contact: <a href="mailto:mrieiqv2@gmail.com">mrieiqv2@gmail.com</a></p>
</main>

